<plot>Jeong-il and Eun-mi have a child together but Jeong-il's family successfully interferes and prevents their marriage. Eun-mi eventually marries, but her husband divorces her when he learns that she has a son. Seeking comfort, Eun-mi goes to her son's school and waits in front to see her boy, but Jeong-il tries to discourage this and does not want her to have any contact with the child.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?043668</url></doc>
